org.jasig.cas.support.saml

Interface SamlProtocolConstants


  • public interface SamlProtocolConstants
    Class that exposes relevant constants and parameters to the SAML protocol. These include attribute names, pre-defined values and expected request parameter names as is specified by the protocol.
    Since:
    4.1
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed
